{"tid":2346843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞笑》舉報台灣youtuber台獨，結果支那小粉紅被公安抓走","createTime":"2020-12-30T14:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T08:41:42.000Z","uid":337052,"like":140,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"917a001ab9d30f64bd57dc219967f5e10f5c5a19","tid":2346843,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">搞笑》舉報台灣youtuber台獨，結果支那小粉紅被公安抓走</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zFgmNHKjBNM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzFgmNHKjBNM&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=d61a918e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zFgmNHKjBNM</a><br />\n<br />\n支那小粉紅上派出所<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8AOfClVdUPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8AOfClVdUPA&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=11388752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8AOfClVdUPA</a>"},{"pid":"0009c97168b7198cca0ff228b8d73a43e7c5b7f2","tid":2346843,"uid":1781,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"On9小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab0e8954cc3c0270cd41c74f0627909f14f3882","tid":2346843,"uid":337052,"like":175,"dislike":0,"score":175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:08:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">孤獨的蒼蠅</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">今天下午針對我非法翻牆使用VPN在派出所接受了民警同志的深刻教育</span>，我也學習了有關的法律知識，在此之後，我也進行了深刻的反省，希望民警同志可以原諒我不懂法的無知行為。<br />\n<br />\n不過好在我翻牆只是為了維護國家和學習的出發點，民警同志並沒有過多為難我，反而還安慰我沒什麼事情，我寫完檢討和保證書，進行相關法律知識的學習後，就返回學校了。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我也對自己犯下的錯誤進行了非常深刻的反省</span>，雖說並不是什麼大錯誤。"},{"pid":"eb7eb3167ac4106ac8a7fa56bb6505f569f80c62","tid":2346843,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1d77261138b32268904246af895213e2f3c6d6","tid":2346843,"uid":331631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5918f1c6d38b210f867a66fb5038135c7c8b2c06","tid":2346843,"uid":337052,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"孤獨的蒼蠅<br />\n<br />\n今天，我懷著愧疚和懊悔發表這個普法視頻，<span class=\"red\">向派出所的民警同志表示我對非法&quot;翻牆&rdquo;違反《計算機信息網絡國際聯網管理暫行規定》的這種不良行為的深刻認識。</span><br />\n<br />\n這是一次十分深刻的檢查，我對於我這次犯的錯誤感到很慚愧，我作為學生，而不懂法律，我感到很抱歉，我希望民警同志可以原諒我的錯誤，我這次的悔過真的很深刻，<span class=\"red\">我發誓我會杜絕一切向國家法律進行挑戰的不良行為。</span><br />\n<br />\n希望老師和民警同志可以原諒我的錯誤，<span class=\"red\">我發誓今後一定不會再使用非法國際聯網工具翻牆上外網。</span>"},{"pid":"02d761ae91b44fdfc56f37c1d5d4d9e160a6d096","tid":2346843,"uid":257216,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"Nm笑sl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d855ba65ec8b2028ccf1658008b88c8de74401","tid":2346843,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:13:37.000Z","msg":"自作孽"},{"pid":"c63011ad3d28915447cbd04a82e193782ea1e13a","tid":2346843,"uid":337052,"like":154,"dislike":0,"score":154,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:15:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fsM0E81Ac8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfsM0E81Ac8I&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=2c78ef01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fsM0E81Ac8I</a><br />\n如何舉報翻牆小粉紅？邀請專家來教各位，幫助牠找到回家的路｜波特王"},{"pid":"93861d26c26804e0669dece78fdc6d06034869ee","tid":2346843,"uid":9230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"胡叼盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\